---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shipping and Delivery Policy" description="Read the Shipping and Delivery Policy of Global Yoga Tips. Learn how our digital products are delivered.">
  <!-- Top Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-secondary-bg/30 border-b border-border-main/40 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary tracking-wider">Compliance</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main">Shipping and Delivery Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Effective date: June 22, 2026. Important information regarding the delivery of your yoga courses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Shipping Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white border border-border-main rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
      <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-text-secondary text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-0 mb-4">1. Digital Delivery Only</h2>
        <p>
          Global Yoga Tips offers **only digital products**. We do not sell or ship physical goods. Therefore, there are no physical shipping addresses, tracking numbers, or physical delivery times associated with our purchases.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">2. Instant Delivery</h2>
        <p>
          As soon as your payment transaction is completed through our secure payment gateway partner:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Dashboard Provisioning:</strong> The premium yoga program or self-care calendar you purchased will be instantly unlocked on your user account dashboard. You can access it by logging in at <a href="/login" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">globalyogatips.com/login</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Email Confirmation:</strong> You will receive a transaction receipt and program access link via the email address you provided during the registration/checkout process. This email is sent within **5 minutes** of a successful payment.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">3. Troubleshooting Delivery Issues</h2>
        <p>
          If you have purchased a program but do not see it unlocked on your dashboard or have not received the confirmation email:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Check your email's **Spam, Junk, or Promotions folder** to ensure the welcome email was not filtered.</li>
          <li>Ensure that you logged in using the same email address that you used during the checkout process.</li>
          <li>If the issue persists for more than 15 minutes, please contact our support team immediately. We will verify your transaction and manually provision access to your account.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">4. Contact Support</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or experience technical difficulties with your product delivery, please reach out to us:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium text-text-main">
          Email: <a href="mailto:support@globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">support@globalyogatips.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
